Install OpenJDK as this is required for Maven to work --> https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/java/openjdk/install

winget search Microsoft.OpenJDK
winget install Microsoft.OpenJDK.21
 
Click this link to download Maven --> https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi

Extract the downloaded zip file.

Follow the instructions to update the environment variables as there is no installation is needed --> https://phoenixnap.com/kb/install-maven-windows


